title: Man-Cave | Watch: Luke Fitzgerald's swing has a touch of the Happy Gilmores
text:
Don't give up the day sport, Luke.
Talented sports people often have a natural physical ability, any great co-ordination, which allows them to float seamlessly between a number of sports.
Luke Fitzgerald is not one of those people, at least not when it comes to golf.
Here he is trying to show some of the Irish team how it's done, and failing miserably.
